## 7. Spacing, padding, gap

### 7.1 Use Tailwind's 4-px scale

| Token | Use |
|---|---|
| `p-1` / `gap-1` (4 px) | Inline icon ↔ chip gap |
| `p-2` / `gap-2` (8 px) | Tag inner padding, tight stack |
| `p-3` / `gap-3` (12 px) | Tool-block padding, drawer body section |
| `p-4` / `gap-4` (16 px) | Card content default, modal body section |
| `p-6` / `gap-6` (24 px) | Card outer padding, drawer content padding, KPI grid gap |
| `p-8` (32 px) | Marketing / hero |

### 7.2 Layout dimensions (set in CSS variables, not per-component)

| Element | Variable / value |
|---|---|
| Top header | `h-14` (56 px) |
| Sidebar width expanded | `--sidebar-width: 220px` (workspace) or `260px` (chat) |
| Sidebar width collapsed | `--sidebar-width-icon: 80px` (workspace) or `56px` (chat) |
| Drawer width | `w-[60%] sm:max-w-none` for log-detail style; `w-[400px]` for narrow side sheets |
| Modal width | `max-w-lg` (520) confirm · `max-w-xl` (576) form · `max-w-3xl` (768) multi-section · `max-w-[90vw]` full-bleed |
| Provider logo (drawer) | `size-6` (24 × 24) |
| Provider logo (table cell) | `size-[18px]` |
| Stop button (chat) | `size-8` rounded-full |
| Inner stop glyph | `size-2.5 rounded-sm` (10 × 10) |
| Send button padding | `px-4 py-1.5` |

- **Do not** invent sidebar / header heights per page. Adjust the CSS variable in `globals.css` and reuse.

### 7.3 Z-index

- **`z-10`**: sticky page header, sticky drawer header, sticky table header.
- **`z-50`**: tooltips, popovers, dropdowns (shadcn defaults).
- **`z-[60]`+**: modals, sheets (shadcn defaults).
- Do not invent intermediate z-index values; choose `10`, `20`, `30`, `40`, `50`, `60`.

### 7.4 Transitions

| Need | Class |
|---|---|
| Hover color/bg swap | `transition-colors` |
| Layout collapse | `transition-[width,grid-template-columns] duration-200 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1)]` |
| Generic | `transition-all duration-150` |

- Use `tw-animate-css` for keyframe-driven animations (already imported).
- **NEVER set `transition:` inline.**

