## 10. Component substitution — mandatory mapping

When you see a LiteLLM pattern (or training-data-default Antd/Tremor pattern) in source you are porting, substitute as below. The full table is in `doc/web-stylng/08-arb-sherpa-mapping.md` §11; the most-used rows:

| Pattern | Use in `PROJECT_NAME` |
|---|---|
| Antd `Modal` | shadcn `Dialog` |
| Antd `Drawer` | shadcn `Sheet` |
| Antd `Tooltip` | shadcn `Tooltip` (requires `<TooltipProvider>` in `AppProviders` — already there) |
| Antd `Popover` | shadcn `Popover` |
| Antd `Switch` / `Radio` | shadcn `Switch` / `RadioGroup` |
| Antd `Tag` / Tremor `Badge` | shadcn `Badge` |
| Antd `Form` | shadcn `Form` (`react-hook-form` + `zod`) |
| Antd `Input` / `Input.TextArea` / Tremor `TextInput` / `Textarea` | shadcn `Input` / `Textarea` |
| Antd `Select` (single) | shadcn `Select` |
| Antd `Select showSearch` | shadcn `Combobox` |
| Antd `Select mode="multiple"` / Tremor `MultiSelect` | shadcn `Combobox` with multi-select or `MultiSelect` from registry |
| Antd `Upload.Dragger` | `react-dropzone` + shadcn styling |
| Antd `notification` | `sonner` (`toast.success/error/warning/info`) |
| Antd `Alert` | shadcn `Alert` |
| Antd `Layout.Sider` + `Menu` | shadcn `Sidebar` + `SidebarMenu` |
| Antd `Typography.Text/Title` | semantic HTML + Tailwind |
| Antd `Spin` | `<Loader2 className="size-4 animate-spin" />` |
| Antd `Collapse` / `Panel` | shadcn `Collapsible` |
| Antd `Card` driven by `theme.useToken()` | shadcn `Card` + tinted variant (see §4 of this file's component rules below, and `doc/web-stylng/06-components/17-themed-cards-error.md`) |
| Tremor `Card` / `Title` / `Text` / `Metric` | shadcn `Card`, semantic HTML |
| Tremor `TabGroup`/`TabList`/`Tab`/`TabPanels` | shadcn `Tabs`/`TabsList`/`TabsTrigger`/`TabsContent` |
| Tremor `Table*` + `@tanstack/react-table` | shadcn `Table*` + `@tanstack/react-table` (keep tanstack) |
| Tremor `BarChart`/`LineChart`/`DonutChart`/`AreaChart` | shadcn `Chart*` (Recharts) |
| Tremor `Button` (any variant) | shadcn `Button` (`variant="default" | "outline" | "ghost" | "destructive" | "link"`) |
| Tremor `Icon variant="shadow"` | shadcn `Button variant="ghost" size="icon"` + lucide icon |
| `react-syntax-highlighter style={coy}` | same lib, swap to `oneDark` (dark default) |
| `react-json-view-lite defaultStyles` | same lib, swap to `darkStyles` |

If a pattern is missing from this table, **read** `doc/web-stylng/08-arb-sherpa-mapping.md` before improvising.

